4
00:00:12,038 --> 00:00:12,998
Jeong-in.

5
00:00:16,042 --> 00:00:17,168
Kau juga...

6
00:00:21,965 --> 00:00:23,133
akan meninggalkan kami?

7
00:00:28,638 --> 00:00:32,058
Jika begitu, masih belum terlambat.

8
00:00:35,562 --> 00:00:36,521
Tak apa.

9
00:00:39,816 --> 00:00:40,859
Apa...

10
00:00:42,319 --> 00:00:43,403
Apa maksudmu?

11
00:00:47,282 --> 00:00:48,241
Hei.

12
00:00:49,367 --> 00:00:50,702
Apa yang kau coba bicarakan?

13
00:00:52,787 --> 00:00:54,039
Kenapa kau seperti ini?

14
00:00:55,123 --> 00:00:56,499
Bisakah aku memercayai...

15
00:01:01,629 --> 00:01:02,756
perasaanmu terhadapku?

16
00:01:07,886 --> 00:01:08,970
Katakanlah.

17
00:01:10,930 --> 00:01:11,931
Kau sungguh yakin...

18
00:01:15,185 --> 00:01:16,227
Kau sungguh yakin

19
00:01:17,228 --> 00:01:18,772
perasaanmu takkan berubah?

20
00:01:24,110 --> 00:01:25,111
Maksudmu,

21
00:01:26,363 --> 00:01:27,947
kau tak bisa memercayaiku?

22
00:01:32,827 --> 00:01:34,537
Kutanya, bisakah aku memercayaimu?

23
00:01:37,290 --> 00:01:38,833
Kau kira aku akan berubah?

24
00:01:40,627 --> 00:01:41,628
Entahlah.

25
00:01:44,130 --> 00:01:45,799
Aku tak mungkin tahu.

26
00:01:51,304 --> 00:01:53,348
Kau mabuk. Kita bicara saja besok.

27
00:01:57,686 --> 00:01:59,020
Kau tak bisa menjawabku.

28
00:02:04,109 --> 00:02:05,110
Begitu, ya.

29
00:02:27,382 --> 00:02:28,383
Jeong-in.

30
00:02:34,806 --> 00:02:36,558
Dia minum terlalu banyak hari ini.

31
00:02:36,641 --> 00:02:39,811
Mohon memaklumi.

32
00:02:41,479 --> 00:02:42,730
Hari ini saja,

33
00:02:43,356 --> 00:02:45,024
atau akan terjadi lagi?

34
00:02:46,860 --> 00:02:48,361
Dia lakukan apa saja saat mabuk?

35
00:02:48,987 --> 00:02:50,280
Ada kebiasaan mabuk lainnya?

36
00:02:53,575 --> 00:02:56,995
Ji-ho menyembunyikan keluhan soal diriku?

37
00:02:57,078 --> 00:02:58,079
Tidak sama sekali.

38
00:02:58,580 --> 00:03:01,166
Jika dia tiba-tiba begitu,
bukankah lebih aneh?

39
00:03:01,791 --> 00:03:02,792
Sebenarnya...

40
00:03:04,794 --> 00:03:06,880
Sejujurnya, Yu-mi...

41
00:03:08,590 --> 00:03:09,632
Siapa itu?

42
00:03:14,596 --> 00:03:15,597
Dia

43
00:03:16,598 --> 00:03:17,682
ibunya Eun-u?

44
00:03:23,021 --> 00:03:25,690
- Entah apa aku harus bilang kepadamu...
- Jangan.

45
00:03:28,234 --> 00:03:29,319
Aku tak mau dengar.

46
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:31,863
Aku pergi dahulu.

47
00:03:44,417 --> 00:03:46,211
Apa yang terjadi, Jeong-in?

48
00:03:46,419 --> 00:03:48,087
- Akan kuhubungi.
- Hei.

49
00:03:48,588 --> 00:03:49,839
Ada apa?

50
00:03:49,923 --> 00:03:52,258
- Kubilang, akan kuhubungi.
- Ada apa?

51
00:03:52,342 --> 00:03:53,551
Jeong-in.

52
00:03:54,594 --> 00:03:56,846
- Hei, Jeong-in.
- Aku sungguh tak apa.

53
00:03:57,597 --> 00:03:58,807
Akan kuhubungi. Maaf.

54
00:04:23,623 --> 00:04:27,126
GI-SEOK

55
00:04:38,721 --> 00:04:42,225
APOTEK WOORI

56
00:05:50,251 --> 00:05:51,669
Aku minum sedikit di rumah.

57
00:05:55,131 --> 00:05:56,215
Saat aku minum...

58
00:05:57,675 --> 00:05:58,760
Ada apa?

59
00:06:02,972 --> 00:06:04,098
Aku hanya mau menemuimu.

60
00:06:07,185 --> 00:06:08,811
Kau memikirkan aku karena minum?

61
00:06:11,147 --> 00:06:12,649
Itu bisa jadi alasan juga.

62
00:06:16,069 --> 00:06:17,362
Kau dari mana saja?

63
00:06:18,321 --> 00:06:19,530
Kau tahu jawabannya.

64
00:06:25,161 --> 00:06:26,829
Kau sungguh bisa menerimaku lagi?

65
00:06:29,832 --> 00:06:31,417
Aku pernah mengkhianatimu.

66
00:06:31,918 --> 00:06:33,920
Maukah kau rujuk denganku?

67
00:06:35,046 --> 00:06:36,464
Bagaimana jika aku berkhianat lagi?

68
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:42,345
Apa maksudmu?

69
00:06:42,428 --> 00:06:43,638
Seperti yang kau dengar.

70
00:06:46,307 --> 00:06:48,017
Perasaanku bisa berubah lagi.

71
00:06:50,269 --> 00:06:52,855
Pernah kulakukan, jadi kedua kalinya
harusnya lebih mudah.

72
00:06:56,109 --> 00:06:57,235
Bagaimana?

73
00:07:00,405 --> 00:07:01,572
Kau bisa percaya padaku?

74
00:07:16,879 --> 00:07:17,714
Ya, aku bisa.

75
00:07:50,997 --> 00:07:52,832
Kenapa Pak Yu belum datang?

76
00:07:53,750 --> 00:07:55,001
Haruskah kutelepon dia?

77
00:07:55,460 --> 00:07:57,545
Jangan. Dia bilang akan datang terlambat.

78
00:08:01,966 --> 00:08:03,509
- Halo.
- Halo.

79
00:08:05,511 --> 00:08:06,387
Tak masalah.

80
00:08:55,019 --> 00:08:57,188
YEONG-JAE

81
00:08:58,231 --> 00:09:00,483
- Hei.
<i>- Kau di apotek?</i>

82
00:09:02,401 --> 00:09:03,444
Tidak, belum.

83
00:09:04,112 --> 00:09:05,530
<i>Kau minum banyak semalam.</i>

84
00:09:08,908 --> 00:09:09,909
Semalam...

85
00:09:10,868 --> 00:09:12,078
Bagaimana Jeong-in pulang?

86
00:09:13,579 --> 00:09:14,747
<i>Kau tak ingat apa pun?</i>

87
00:09:17,375 --> 00:09:19,001
Tak semuanya, tapi...

88
00:09:20,753 --> 00:09:22,797
Aku tak bilang yang aneh-aneh, 'kan?

89
00:09:23,381 --> 00:09:24,507
<i>Kau sudah gila?</i>

90
00:09:25,258 --> 00:09:27,093
<i>Kau bilang tak bisa memercayainya</i>

91
00:09:27,510 --> 00:09:30,012
<i>dan bertanya akankah dia
meninggalkanmu dan Eun-u.</i>

92
00:09:31,139 --> 00:09:33,099
Begitukah? Aku bilang itu?

93
00:09:33,182 --> 00:09:35,518
<i>Lantas? Kau bilang itu kepadaku?</i>

94
00:09:36,185 --> 00:09:37,645
<i>Dia tampaknya salah paham,</i>

95
00:09:37,728 --> 00:09:40,523
<i>jadi, aku menyebutkan Yu-mi...</i>

96
00:09:40,606 --> 00:09:42,775
Itu tak penting.
Kenapa bilang begitu padanya?

97
00:09:43,317 --> 00:09:45,319
<i>Aku tak beri tahu dia
karena tak dia izinkan.</i>

98
00:09:45,403 --> 00:09:46,654
<i>Dia tak mau dengar.</i>

99
00:09:49,824 --> 00:09:52,160
<i>Kenapa kau tunjukkan
jika mau kau sembunyikan?</i>

100
00:09:52,243 --> 00:09:53,995
<i>Kau menggila.</i>

101
00:10:08,509 --> 00:10:09,677
Teleponmu terus berbunyi.

102
00:10:10,469 --> 00:10:12,430
- Kurasa sudah ditutup.
- Terima kasih.

103
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:27,528
Kau tahu? Manajer tak suka laporanku lagi.

104
00:10:27,612 --> 00:10:29,071
Itu membuatku kesal,

105
00:10:29,155 --> 00:10:31,824
jadi, kuubah beberapa hal
dan berikan lagi padanya.

106
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:36,746
- Dia langsung senang, ya?
- Benar!

107
00:10:38,122 --> 00:10:39,707
Dia selalu begitu.

108
00:10:42,001 --> 00:10:43,377
Aku pernah tertangkap basah.

109
00:10:44,211 --> 00:10:45,588
Kau tahu dia bilang apa?

110
00:10:46,213 --> 00:10:47,298
"Konon,

111
00:10:47,965 --> 00:10:50,134
yang pertama selalu yang terbaik.

112
00:10:50,593 --> 00:10:53,262
Pilihan pertama
yang kau ambil selalu benar."

113
00:10:56,807 --> 00:10:58,017
Kau kenal dia lebih baik.

114
00:11:01,979 --> 00:11:03,105
Aku sering mengalaminya.

115
00:11:17,244 --> 00:11:19,705
Apa? Kau kira aku Ji-ho?

116
00:11:30,716 --> 00:11:32,718
Kau bergadang semalaman,
tapi tetap ke kantor

117
00:11:32,843 --> 00:11:34,470
dan tak makan siang.

118
00:11:35,471 --> 00:11:36,764
Jadi, apa kesimpulannya?

119
00:11:39,642 --> 00:11:40,977
Aku tak bisa menyimpulkan.

120
00:11:42,770 --> 00:11:44,814
Apa yang paling mengusikmu?

121
00:11:45,564 --> 00:11:46,941
Ibunya anak itu?

122
00:11:47,358 --> 00:11:48,859
Kalau dia masih mengharapkannya?

123
00:11:50,736 --> 00:11:51,988
Itu mustahil.

124
00:11:53,072 --> 00:11:54,740
Jika dia masih punya perasaan,

125
00:11:54,824 --> 00:11:57,326
Ji-ho...
Astaga, menurutku dia sangat bodoh.

126
00:11:57,910 --> 00:11:59,078
Dia tak punya harga diri?

127
00:12:01,414 --> 00:12:02,540
Lalu Gi-seok?

128
00:12:03,082 --> 00:12:04,583
Itu hanya obsesi.

129
00:12:08,087 --> 00:12:10,256
Ji-ho bilang, dia tak bisa memercayaiku,

130
00:12:11,090 --> 00:12:12,299
tapi Gi-seok bisa.

131
00:12:13,759 --> 00:12:15,469
Bukankah seharusnya sebaliknya?

132
00:12:17,221 --> 00:12:18,973
Mungkin memang ditakdirkan sebaliknya.

133
00:12:19,348 --> 00:12:20,683
Kau mulai melantur.

134
00:12:21,934 --> 00:12:24,020
Kau mau salahkan Ji-ho dan melarikan diri?

135
00:12:25,688 --> 00:12:26,897
Akan kupertimbangkan.

136
00:12:29,191 --> 00:12:30,568
Ada satu hal yang jelas.

137
00:12:32,862 --> 00:12:36,365
Kurasa aku hanya melihat
apa yang ada di hadapanku.

138
00:12:37,491 --> 00:12:38,576
Namun, kau tahu,

139
00:12:39,910 --> 00:12:42,246
mengetahui semua soal masa lalu seseorang

140
00:12:43,289 --> 00:12:44,915
tak selalu ada baiknya.

141
00:12:45,708 --> 00:12:48,794
Lebih baik pura-pura tak tahu
dan lupakan yang sudah lewat.

142
00:12:50,546 --> 00:12:52,131
Dan saling mencurigai?

143
00:12:54,467 --> 00:12:56,177
Ji-ho mungkin tak keberatan.

144
00:12:56,761 --> 00:12:59,096
Namun, dari sifatmu, kau pasti keberatan.

145
00:13:33,881 --> 00:13:36,926
APOTEK WOORI

146
00:13:44,767 --> 00:13:46,685
- Sampai jumpa.
- Terima kasih.

147
00:13:49,146 --> 00:13:50,981
- Ini.
- Terima kasih.

148
00:13:51,899 --> 00:13:53,359
- Nona Yun Mi-sun.
- Ya.

149
00:13:55,653 --> 00:13:56,487
Ini...

150
00:13:59,031 --> 00:14:00,574
- Minumlah setelah makan.
- Baik.

151
00:14:40,448 --> 00:14:41,490
Hei.

152
00:14:42,992 --> 00:14:45,035
- Kita bicara di tempat lain.
- Soal apa?

153
00:14:57,756 --> 00:14:58,757
<i>Halo?</i>

154
00:14:59,842 --> 00:15:00,843
Hei, Jeong-in.

155
00:15:01,844 --> 00:15:02,845
<i>Hei.</i>

156
00:15:04,597 --> 00:15:06,515
Aku sibuk, jadi, tak sempat menelepon.

157
00:15:07,141 --> 00:15:08,100
<i>Tak masalah.</i>

158
00:15:10,603 --> 00:15:12,104
Kau bisa pulang semalam, 'kan?

159
00:15:17,818 --> 00:15:18,694
Begini...

160
00:15:20,946 --> 00:15:22,406
Entah kenapa aku mabuk...

161
00:15:25,910 --> 00:15:26,952
Kau kesal kepadaku, ya?

162
00:15:28,287 --> 00:15:29,663
Aku minum banyak semalam.

163
00:15:32,208 --> 00:15:33,959
Aku salah. Aku sadar akan ucapanku.

164
00:15:34,793 --> 00:15:35,794
Begini...

165
00:15:36,629 --> 00:15:38,464
Aku tak pernah begitu. Namun, kemarin...

166
00:15:39,965 --> 00:15:41,842
Mari bertemu. Kita bicara langsung.

167
00:15:41,926 --> 00:15:43,093
Aku bisa mampir sekarang,

168
00:15:44,887 --> 00:15:46,764
atau kau yang mampir?

169
00:15:47,473 --> 00:15:49,975
<i>Tidak, kita bertemu di kafe saja.</i>

170
00:16:08,577 --> 00:16:09,703
Hai, Ibu.

171
00:16:10,496 --> 00:16:13,415
<i>Ibu sudah minta untuk datang
atau telepon agar ibu bisa mampir.</i>

172
00:16:14,583 --> 00:16:16,502
Maaf, aku agak sibuk.

173
00:16:17,795 --> 00:16:19,171
Kenapa? Ada apa?

174
00:16:19,838 --> 00:16:22,466
- Ayah bilang apa lagi?
<i>- Dia buat keributan.</i>

175
00:16:24,009 --> 00:16:27,346
<i>Omong-omong, kenapa kau terdengar muram?</i>

176
00:16:28,180 --> 00:16:29,223
Aku baik-baik saja.

177
00:16:30,432 --> 00:16:31,600
Kutemui setelah kelas.

178
00:16:32,810 --> 00:16:34,687
<i>Kelas itu sudah lama berakhir.</i>

179
00:16:35,271 --> 00:16:36,105
Benar juga.

180
00:16:38,107 --> 00:16:39,316
<i>Ibu menghubungi...</i>

181
00:16:40,609 --> 00:16:42,486
<i>untuk membahas pria itu.</i>

182
00:16:42,778 --> 00:16:43,862
Kita bicara lain kali.

183
00:16:44,655 --> 00:16:46,615
Aku mampir saat libur. Kita bicara nanti.

184
00:16:47,741 --> 00:16:49,243
<i>Kenapa menunggu sampai...</i>

185
00:16:49,577 --> 00:16:52,246
Ibu, aku tak bisa mengobrol di telepon.

186
00:16:52,788 --> 00:16:54,748
Kuhubungi saat aku mampir.
Aku tutup dahulu.

187
00:17:06,594 --> 00:17:08,262
Aku bilang hal bodoh pada Jeong-in.

188
00:17:09,054 --> 00:17:10,180
Kau bilang apa?

189
00:17:12,141 --> 00:17:14,893
Kutanya, akankah dia
tinggalkan aku dan Eun-u.

190
00:17:16,395 --> 00:17:17,688
Kau kira dia mau begitu?

191
00:17:18,188 --> 00:17:21,025
- Tentu tidak.
- Lalu kenapa menanyakannya?

192
00:17:22,526 --> 00:17:25,195
Kau tahu aku mabuk berat semalam.

193
00:17:25,779 --> 00:17:27,156
Itu membuatku gila.

194
00:17:28,157 --> 00:17:30,659
Kau tampak manusiawi. Bagus sekali.

195
00:17:31,619 --> 00:17:32,661
Apa maksudmu?

196
00:17:33,162 --> 00:17:35,706
Selama ini kau seperti robot,
serasa duniamu akan hancur

197
00:17:36,290 --> 00:17:37,958
jika kau bersikap santai.

198
00:17:38,626 --> 00:17:40,669
Kau tampak bisa dipercaya,
tapi tak manusiawi.

199
00:17:43,505 --> 00:17:45,841
- Itu salah?
- Bukan hal yang bagus.

200
00:17:46,383 --> 00:17:48,761
Yang kau tunjukkan kepadanya
bukan diri aslimu.

201
00:17:50,929 --> 00:17:51,847
Coba sangkal.

202
00:17:54,266 --> 00:17:57,686
Sebelum itu...
Aku harus bagaimana terhadap Jeong-in?

203
00:18:00,856 --> 00:18:02,691
Walau kau terbebani masa lalu,

204
00:18:03,442 --> 00:18:05,944
pasti akan lebih berat bagi Jeong-in.

205
00:18:08,113 --> 00:18:12,493
Jangan harap dia memahami semuanya.
Itu lebih dari sekadar keegoisan.

206
00:18:41,146 --> 00:18:44,233
Kau tak mau bicara,
atau tak ada yang mau dibicarakan?

207
00:18:50,239 --> 00:18:51,365
Haruskah kuulangi?

208
00:18:53,283 --> 00:18:54,868
Kau tak punya alasan,

209
00:18:55,577 --> 00:18:58,664
atau tak bisa memikirkannya
karena tak ingat apa pun?

210
00:19:03,419 --> 00:19:04,461
Menurutku, keduanya.

211
00:19:10,008 --> 00:19:11,176
Bukankah tak mungkin

212
00:19:11,969 --> 00:19:14,096
tak ingat apa pun walau kau sangat mabuk?

213
00:19:18,225 --> 00:19:20,102
Ini terdengar seperti alasan,

214
00:19:21,562 --> 00:19:23,397
tapi aku mengatakan itu karena mabuk.

215
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:25,190
Menurutmu, aku anggap kau begitu?

216
00:19:26,191 --> 00:19:27,401
Lalu kau anggap aku apa?

217
00:19:31,405 --> 00:19:32,614
Maafkan aku.

218
00:19:34,450 --> 00:19:35,743
Aku sungguh minta maaf.

219
00:19:36,910 --> 00:19:39,872
Aku tak pernah menduga
kau akan lakukan hal semacam itu.

220
00:19:40,289 --> 00:19:41,331
Aku serius.

221
00:19:43,208 --> 00:19:44,918
Meninggalkan aku dan Eun-u...

222
00:19:47,004 --> 00:19:48,630
Aku bahkan malu membahasnya.

223
00:19:49,798 --> 00:19:52,301
Aku tak pernah membayangkannya.

224
00:19:54,219 --> 00:19:55,220
Ya, 'kan?

225
00:19:56,221 --> 00:19:57,264
Namun, kau bertanya,

226
00:20:00,184 --> 00:20:01,894
akankah aku meninggalkanmu juga?

227
00:20:03,979 --> 00:20:07,316
"Akankah aku meninggalkanmu juga?"
Itu pertanyaanmu.

228
00:20:11,403 --> 00:20:12,988
Aku tahu aku mencari kesalahan.

229
00:20:13,864 --> 00:20:15,240
Mungkin aku salah mengira.

230
00:20:17,618 --> 00:20:19,620
Sejujurnya, kesan yang kudapat adalah...

231
00:20:22,498 --> 00:20:24,750
"Bukankah kau sama seperti dia?"
Terdengar begitu.

232
00:20:30,547 --> 00:20:32,216
Aku tahu kau tak bermaksud begitu.

233
00:20:33,091 --> 00:20:34,885
Seperti kataku, itu kesan yang kudapat.

234
00:20:40,849 --> 00:20:42,267
Aku tak pernah menganggap

235
00:20:43,894 --> 00:20:45,395
lukamu pulih sepenuhnya

